            "id": "688bf1fa09622700019c57d7",
            "title": "Here&#39;s How Much $1000 Invested In Starbucks 15 Years Ago Would Be Worth Today",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-dhlHIi fuaxyy\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Starbucks <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"SBUX\" style=\"display:inline-block\">SBUX</span> has outperformed the market over the past 15 years by 1.69% on an annualized basis producing an average annual return of 13.89%. Currently, Starbucks has a market capitalization of $101.62 billion. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Buying $1000 In SBUX:</strong> If an investor had bought $1000 of SBUX stock 15 years ago, it would be worth <strong>$7,081.81</strong> today based on a price of $89.40 for SBUX at the time of writing.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-dGJnDi cqLODL\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold\">Trending Investment Opportunities</div><div class=\"flex items-end justify-end\"><div class=\"text-right text-sm bg-gray-200 rounded px-2 py-1\">Advertisement</div></div></div></div><div class=\"cta-stacked GalleryCarousel_splide_slidewrap__zHpTC\"><div class=\"sc-cwcSVF hlcLHF carousel-container\"><div aria-label=\"Carousel\" class=\"splide\"><div class=\"splide-track-wrapper\"><div class=\"splide__track\"><ul class=\"splide__list\"><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"carousel-pagination\"><div class=\"splide__arrows\"><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev page-left-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\"